high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink to your left.
Pick up a knife from the sink.
Turn around, walk straight to the door, and then turn left to the fridge.
Cut the tomato in the fridge into slices and close the fridge.
Take a step backwards, and open the fridge again.
Place the knife on the shelf below the tomato and close the fridge.
Take a step forward, and open the fridge again.
Take out a slice of tomato from the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the counter.
Place the slice of tomato on the left plate near the plant.
Pick up the plate with the tomato from the counter.
Turn around, walk to the door, and then turn left to the fridge.
Place the plate next  to the cut tomato in the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a cooled slice tomato in the fridge along with a knife.

Take the knife out of the sink.

Put the knife in the refrigerator and close the door.
